Nothing, Solly.

18
00:02:15,265 --> 00:02:17,049
Seen my Uncle Eddie anywhere?

19
00:02:17,093 --> 00:02:18,181
I'm willing to bet he's

20
00:02:18,225 --> 00:02:19,487
over there at the barn

