22
00:02:21,706 --> 00:02:23,230
that hard-luck horse of yours.

23
00:02:23,273 --> 00:02:24,883
Thanks.

24
00:02:24,927 --> 00:02:26,146
Now, you see your uncle,

25
00:02:26,189 --> 00:02:27,669
you tell him to call me.

26
00:02:27,712 --> 00:02:29,061
I got some business to discuss

27
00:02:29,105 --> 00:02:30,628
