87
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:50,464
Ever known me to be wrong?

88
00:04:58,385 --> 00:04:59,037
Don't spend it all

89
00:04:59,081 --> 00:05:00,822
in one place, okay?

90
00:05:04,129 --> 00:05:06,523
Say, what do you know about

91
00:05:06,567 --> 00:05:08,525
a horse named Manifest Wind?

92
00:05:08,569 --> 00:05:10,484
Slauson bred, MacVie trained.

93
00:05:10,527 --> 00:05:11,354
Royal blood on both sides

94
00:05:11,398 --> 00:05:12,442
of the family, probably a

95
00:05:12,486 --> 00:05:14,139
contender for the Tucker Stakes.

96
00:05:14,183 --> 00:05:15,315
They were parading him in

97
00:05:15,358 --> 00:05:16,620
front of the press this morning.

98
00:05:16,664 --> 00:05:17,534
Yeah, he's running in the

99
00:05:17,578 --> 00:05:19,406
seventh today, first race ever.

100
00:05:19,449 --> 00:05:21,103
They trained him off track.

101
00:05:21,146 --> 00:05:22,060
[scoffs] I wouldn't touch that

102
